{"tid":1819160,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(live)河內六日五夜玩水之旅","createTime":"2020-01-10T14:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T13:50:26.000Z","uid":208017,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8d54654609755e12d9d4989ba185254d99a14d93","tid":1819160,"uid":208017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"其實我唔想玩水架diu<br />\n而家睇天氣報告中間四日full day(14-17)全部都係落大雨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94MNJnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94MNJnD.png&h=707f0534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我早幾日訂既時候已經知係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請教下唱錢應該帶美金去當地金行定銀卡撳錢好?<br />\n上次去峴港喺重慶大廈直接唱越南盾，我到到而家都未知個rate係賺咗定畀人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電話卡打算去鴨記買一張40蚊玩下，到時機場用唔到再買一張<br />\n話說上次去到機場買左張4G，最後全程都係3G但叫用到google map<br />\n今次都有心理準備俾人呃<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩食野地方係推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，會喺河內同寧平stay兩日<br />\n條街冇水浸我都會租26揸，如果唔係卓明樓我都會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91797f788f2db5f409cca520877b0fb66eb202a","tid":1819160,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fcead6f60fb774d2b1fe5bcbfd752303156bbc","tid":1819160,"uid":300956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"vip massage<br />\n求其入一間都好好服務"},{"pid":"1b670d1973d4a671daed14be93b20a79f74392a6","tid":1819160,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"我3年前都係1月去. <br />\n去咗9日, 落足9日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩我著晒成身GORE-TEX 去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72316b7c55d3acfb1165b8f6399b51781a3b6dd","tid":1819160,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit